forked from ComputerNerd/ov7670-no-ram-arduino-uno

modified for:
Arduino Mega 2560
Arduino Software (IDE)

Connections:
Arduino Mega - OV7670
21 -(level shift!)-> SIOC
20 <-(level shift!)-> SIOD
46 -(level shift!)-> XCLK
30 <- D7
31 <- D6
32 <- D5
33 <- D4
34 <- D3
35 <- D2
36 <- D1
37 <- D0
26 <- VSYNC
28 <- PCLK
GND  -> PWDN
3.3v -> RESET
GND  -> GND
3.3v -> 3V3

warning:
don't connect SIOC, SIOD, XCLK directly to arduino mega
consequences will be unpredictable.
Arduino Mega 2560 board has 20, 21 pins pulled-up to 5V! (see scematics)
